## Stable release

To use this version in your project read the following example.

### Maven
`pom.xml`
```xml
<project>
	<repositories>

		<!-- Add the following repository -->
		<repository>
			<id>mchv</id>
			<name>MCHV Apache Maven Packages</name>
			<url>https://mvn.mchv.eu/repository/mchv/</url>
		</repository>

	</repositories>

	<dependencyManagement>
		<dependencies>
			
			<!-- Add the following dependency -->
			<dependency>
				<groupId>it.tdlight</groupId>
				<artifactId>tdlight-java-bom</artifactId>
				<version>2.8.5.1</version>
				<type>pom</type>
				<scope>import</scope>
			</dependency>
		</dependencies>
	</dependencyManagement>

	<dependencies>

		<!-- Add the following dependencies -->
		<dependency>
			<groupId>it.tdlight</groupId>
			<artifactId>tdlight-java</artifactId>
			<!-- don't specify the version here -->
		</dependency>
		<dependency>
			<groupId>it.tdlight</groupId>
			<artifactId>tdlight-natives-linux-amd64</artifactId>
			<!-- don't specify the version here -->
		</dependency>
		<!-- Include other native versions that you want, for example for windows, osx, ... -->

	</dependencies>
</project>
```

### Gradle
`build.gradle`
```groovy
repositories {
	maven { url "https://mvn.mchv.eu/repository/mchv/" }
}
dependencies {
	// import the BOM
	implementation platform('it.tdlight:tdlight-java-bom:2.8.5.1')

	// do not specify the versions on the dependencies below!
	implementation 'it.tdlight:tdlight-java'
	implementation 'it.tdlight:tdlight-natives-linux-amd64'
	// Include other native versions that you want, for example for windows, osx, ...
}
```

Installing with maven:

```xml
<project>
    <repositories>
        <repository>
            <id>mchv</id>
            <name>MCHV Apache Maven Packages</name>
            <url>https://mvn.mchv.eu/repository/mchv/</url>
        </repository>
    </repositories>

    <dependencies>
        <dependency>
            <groupId>it.tdlight</groupId>
            <artifactId>tdlight-java</artifactId>
            <version>2.7.8.20</version>
        </dependency>
        <dependency>
            <groupId>it.tdlight</groupId>
            <artifactId>tdlight-natives-linux-amd64</artifactId>
            <version>3.3.161</version>
        </dependency>
        <!-- Include other native versions that you want, for example for windows, osx, ... -->
    </dependencies>
</project>
```
#### Gradle
```groovy
repositories {
     maven { url "https://mvn.mchv.eu/repository/mchv/" }
}
dependencies {
     implementation 'it.tdlight:tdlight-java:2.7.8.20'
     implementation 'it.tdlight:tdlight-natives-linux-amd64:3.3.161'
     // Include other native versions that you want, for example for windows, osx, ...
}
```
